    "description": "Do you have the skills to beat this challenging game? <br>Help a cute armadillo get to the top of the mountain, be careful with every step or you can find yourself rolling back to the bottom of it!<br>Only a few players have achieved it so far, will you be the next one?<br>Rolling Over It is a simulation game in which you take control of an armadillo shaped as a sphere. The gameplay consists on using the mouse's  point and click to calculate your next move's trajectory, helping the armadillo climb platforms and slopes. <br>This game is about precision, too much or too little force applied when launching the armadillo may end up with it rolling down to the bottom!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892510/extras/cbe9c7efbae327e34eca805e43e1f635.poster.avif?t=1645814318\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892510/extras/cbe9c7efbae327e34eca805e43e1f635.webm?t=1645814318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892510/extras/cbe9c7efbae327e34eca805e43e1f635.mp4?t=1645814318\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
